Recorded at the London Perl Workshop 2010

IO::Async is a framework for building event-driven programs, based on the idea of continuations.

If you're thinking of attending this talk, you possibly also want the talk on CPS; http://conferences.yapceurope.org/lpw2010/talk/3109
